OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fevening sunshine away from the coast,
OL,7,Fshowers could linger through the night
OL,8,Fwith a rumble of thunder possible.
OL,9,FOvernight the patchy low cloud may
OL,10,Fspread inland, with some hill fog
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAn outbreak of showers is
OL,14,Fpossible early in the morning, with
OL,15,Fany low cloud or hill fog quickly
OL,16,Fclearing away. Then another dry day
OL,17,Fwith sunny intervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
